<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#333333;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;">
  Your verification code
</h2>

<p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#555555;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
  Use the code below to verify your identity on Social Bounty. This code expires in 5 minutes.
</p>

<div style="text-align:center;margin:0 0 24px;">
  <div style="display:inline-block;background-color:#f0f0f5;border:2px solid #e0e0e8;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 32px;letter-spacing:8px;font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a2e;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;">
    {{otp}}
  </div>
</div>

<p style="margin:0 0 8px;color:#555555;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">
  If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<p style="margin:0;color:#999999;font-size:13px;">
  Do not share this code with anyone. Social Bounty will never ask for your code.
</p>
